* encoding="UTF-8"
* DAMOS format
* Test file for 2D map diff testing - MODIFIED

KONSERVIERUNG_FORMAT 2.0

* Modified 2D map for testing
* Changes:
* 1. LANGNAME changed from "Base 2D calibration map" to "Modified 2D calibration map"
* 2. X axis var changed from AXIS_X_001 to AXIS_X_002
* 3. Y axis var changed from AXIS_Y_001 to AXIS_Y_002
* 4. X axis points changed from 6 to 5
* 5. Y axis points changed from 4 to 3
* 6. Table values changed
GRUPPENKENNFELD MAP_TEST_001 5 3
   LANGNAME "Modified 2D calibration map"
   EINHEIT_X "deg/s"
   EINHEIT_Y "km/h"
   EINHEIT_W "mA"
*SSTX	AXIS_X_002
*SSTY	AXIS_Y_002
   ST/X   -8.0000000000000000   -4.0000000000000000   0.0000000000000000   4.0000000000000000   8.0000000000000000
   ST/Y   0.0000000000000000
   WERT   105.0000000000000000   115.0000000000000000   125.0000000000000000   135.0000000000000000   145.0000000000000000
   ST/Y   25.0000000000000000
   WERT   205.0000000000000000   225.0000000000000000   245.0000000000000000   265.0000000000000000   285.0000000000000000
   ST/Y   50.0000000000000000
   WERT   305.0000000000000000   335.0000000000000000   365.0000000000000000   395.0000000000000000   415.0000000000000000
END

* New axis distributions (with different point counts)
STUETZSTELLENVERTEILUNG AXIS_X_002 5
*SST
   LANGNAME "Modified X axis distribution"
   EINHEIT_X "deg/s"
   ST/X   -8.0000000000000000   -4.0000000000000000   0.0000000000000000   4.0000000000000000   8.0000000000000000
END

STUETZSTELLENVERTEILUNG AXIS_Y_002 3
*SST
   LANGNAME "Modified Y axis distribution"
   EINHEIT_X "km/h"
   ST/X   0.0000000000000000   25.0000000000000000   50.0000000000000000
END
